             Asked at: TCS, Wipro, Capgemini

  [C][ ] (E) Replace each element with the greatest element on its right side
             e.g. [17,18,5,4,6,1] -> [18,6,6,6,1,-1]
             Asked at: Amazon, LeetCode Easy

  [C][ ] (E) Find the index of the first occurrence of the minimum element
             Asked at: TCS, Wipro

  [C][ ] (E) Separate odd and even numbers — odds first, evens after (any order within groups)
